# React / Next.js Standards

- Use App Router (Next.js 14+)
- Components: Shadcn/ui + Tailwind, server components preferred.
- State: Zustand / Jotai over Redux for simplicity.
- Data fetching: Server actions > API routes when possible.
- Accessibility: ARIA labels, keyboard nav basics.
- SEO: Metadata API, dynamic OG images.